{"tid":464500,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左，發現玩gal game先係自己既歸宿.......","createTime":"2017-11-10T14:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T07:10:46.000Z","uid":75100,"like":57,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b52fcf34cc8ffdcd2b147ec934a5f4525dc1aa4f","tid":464500,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"係現實，有時付出係無收獲........無論係溝女定係識朋友.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n但係gal game入面，你無論再唔顯眼，再平凡，都會有唔同既女仔男仔主動接近你，同你一齊做好多野，令你既生活變得多姿多采，編寫一個又一個既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要你選項無簡錯，你最後一定可以同其中一位女主角開花結果，你同個女仔可以有好多刻骨銘心既回憶.......有好多劇情，係無論幾靚仔既人，現實都無可能體驗到........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個gal game既男主角既身邊，多數都會有一個死黨 .......佢可以幫你助攻溝女, 平時同你傾計，必要時就算自己會受傷，都要為你出頭，就好似white album 2既武也咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實自己係個有無都得既小人物，但係Gal game入面，我就係全個世界，係世界既軸心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我可以同好多人結立起牽絆，有好多神奇既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩得多之後，我發現自己已經去到桂木桂馬咁既心境了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實單身不知幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5665035768652f4473e962daff775d7b6cd235b","tid":464500,"uid":75100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"二次元，I am  back！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n動漫，gal game，小說，figure買完玩完睇完就一世永遠係自己的了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fec316838a26a3bc843c8e3e92c8159cb8b2d77","tid":464500,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"樓主金毛飛"},{"pid":"c75a10a00fabed5e7f94568df792bfcde46b885f","tid":464500,"uid":75100,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主金毛飛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭髮既顏色，係唔會改變到我係純真毒撚既事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03823e51bc7c95f0bdcb58102366390913fab6c2","tid":464500,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7da8c447c8a52d88760089bb12f70d03c99530","tid":464500,"uid":8307,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"樓主=clannad入面個金毛"},{"pid":"58aae38008696b0e1f914adf93c101a5ea3d0784","tid":464500,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主=clannad入面個金毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要比智代打爆又要睇住朋也溝哂女，我唔想做佢wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做ntr金毛得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa970bb1d0553016aa06c42c6bdc53a6482d38a3","tid":464500,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主金毛飛</blockquote>"},{"pid":"98957be72e33a8154db4396403b20e5f58b67019","tid":464500,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主=clannad入面個金毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要比智代打爆又要睇住朋也溝哂女，我唔想做佢wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做ntr金毛得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比智代踢係享受!"},{"pid":"9101ca52432bd785f0227859de73ddf228a550a2","tid":464500,"uid":673,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/230941_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F230941_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228